step.command:
import com.electriccloud.client.groovy.ElectricFlow import com.electriccloud.client.groovy.models.*
ElectricFlow ef = new ElectricFlow()
def jira_comment = "$[JIRA_Description]"
if("$[/myStageRuntime/outcome]" == "success" && "$[/myJob/outcome]" == "success"){ ef.setProperty(propertyName: "/myJob/jira_issueKey_trans_success", value: "true") jira_comment = jira_comment + "\n$[/myStageRuntime/stageName]: Deploy" jira_comment = jira_comment + "\nCD Pipeline: https://cloudbees.devops.mousoft.co.kr/flow/#pipeline-run/$[/myPipelineRuntime/pipelineId]/$[/myPipelineRuntime/flowRuntimeId]" jira_comment = jira_comment + "\nQA url: http://cloudbees.devops.mousoft.co.kr:8070/univers-web/ui"
}else{ ef.setProperty(propertyName: "/myJob/jira_issueKey_trans_success", value: "true") ef.setProperty(propertyName: "/myJob/jira_issueKey_trans_fail", value: "true") if("$[/myJob/RollbackResult]" == "success"){ jira_comment = "$[/myStageRuntime/stageName]: Rollback" } } ef.setProperty(propertyName : "/myJob/jira_comment", value : "${jira_comment}")
ef.setProperty(propertyName : "/myJob/jira_description", value : "${jira_comment}")

def description = "$[/myStageRuntime/stageName]:" + "$[/myStageRuntime/outcome]\n" description = description + "$[JIRA_COMMENT]"
